title: YöL Set of 3 Ice Lolly Plush Pet Dog Toy Squeaker Crinkle Effect Absorbs Water Hydrating Cooling Summer Stimulating Play
features: TOY: These soft and cuddly plush toys are perfect for interactive games of throw and fetch, providing endless entertainment while encouraging exercise and bonding between pets and their owners.

SQUEAKER: Designed with an internal squeaker and crinkle material, these toys engage your pet’s natural instincts, stimulating playtime while helping to prevent boredom and promoting mental stimulation.

DURABLE: Made from high-quality polyester, these plush toys are designed for durability while maintaining a soft and gentle texture, ensuring they are both long-lasting and comfortable for your pet to chew and cuddle.
SIZE: With approximate body measurements of 22cm x 9cm, these toys are an ideal size for various breeds, making them suitable for both small and medium-sized pets to enjoy.
COLOUR: Available in three vibrant assorted designs—rainbow, pink, and watermelon—these colorful and playful plush toys add a fun and visually appealing element to your pet’s toy collection.
description: Product Description Squeaky Ice Lolly Toys These soft plush toys are perfect for throwing and fetching games, keeping pets entertained while encouraging exercise and bonding with their owners. Each toy features a squeaker and crinkle material to stimulate your pet’s natural instincts and reduce boredom. Made from durable yet gentle polyester, they’re great for chewing and cuddling. Measuring 22cm x 9cm, they suit small to medium breeds and come in three fun designs: rainbow, pink, and watermelon. Plush Sea Life Toys These sea-themed plush toys are designed for engaging hide-and-seek play, encouraging pets to sniff, search, and discover hidden surprises for hours of fun. Built-in squeakers and crinkle material stimulate natural instincts and keep pets mentally active. Made from durable yet soft polyester, they’re gentle on mouths and ideal for everyday play. Measuring 30cm x 15cm, they come in three colourful designs: pink jellyfish, orange seahorse, and blue whale. Plush Rope Toys These plush and rope toys are perfect for tug-of-war, fetch, or solo play, keeping pets active and engaged. Each toy features built-in squeakers and an ice cream-themed design with three plush cones connected by a strong rope. Made from soft polyester and durable rope, they’re gentle on mouths yet tough enough for extended use. With sizes up to 40cm, they suit various breeds and play styles. Available in three vibrant designs, they offer fun, comfort, and stimulation. Treat Hiding Toy Turn treat time into an exciting game of hide and seek with these summer-themed plush toys, designed to stimulate your dog’s natural foraging instincts. Each set includes a crinkle-lined plush bag and three squeaky fruit toys—perfect for hiding treats and encouraging playful exploration. Made from durable polyester, the bag measures 25cm x 19cm x 6cm, while the fruits are 13cm x 7cm. With fun designs like strawberry, lime, and orange, playtime becomes both engaging and rewarding.
